data.description: This house is bursting with updates including new carpet and fresh paint! The partially finished basement has been completely renovated, providing lots of extra living space and a place for entertaining.  New roof, furnace, AC and HWT.  New plumbing throughout. All appliances convey, including washer and dryer.  Alley access allows entry to the garage, off street parking and a generously sized fenced in back yard. Too many updates to list!!
